powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.prestige_Pocket_D_VIP_Pass
powers.display_help: You've been given a VIP Pass to Pocket D. It will allow you to access Pocket D from anywhere. It is usable once every 30 minutes.

powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.prestige_Base_Teleport
powers.display_help: You have a Base Transport beacon. It will allow you to return to your base from any location. It is usable once every 30 minutes.

powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.prestige_Mission_Teleport
powers.display_help: You have a Mission Transport beacon. It will allow you to teleport to your active mission's entrance. Note that Mission Transporter is unaffected by Recharge Time changes

powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.Team_Transporter
powers.display_help: Activating this power will summon a vehicle that will allow your party to teleport to the active mission. This power cannot be activated while on a PvP or mission map. Note that Team Transporter is unaffected by Recharge Time changes

powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.prestige_Team_Recall
powers.display_help: This power allows you to teleport all of your teammates to your location. Note that Assemble the Team is unaffected by Recharge Time changes

powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.Prestige_Ninja_Run
powers.display_help: A combination of quickness and acrobatic grace, Ninja Run allows you to move at high speed, whether on the ground or leaping from rooftop to rooftop. This power is not as fast as Super Speed, nor will it allow you to jump as well as Super Leap, however it is considerably better than the Fitness powers Swift and Hurdle.

powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.Prestige_Beast_Run
powers.display_help: Show off your bestial nature by using this power. This power is not as fast as Super Speed, nor will it allow you to jump as well as Super Leap, however it is considerably better than the Fitness powers Swift and Hurdle.

powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.Prestige_Steam_Jump
powers.display_help: Your steam powered jump pack grants you the ability to not only jump great distances, but also jump and gain altitude in mid air! The steam powered jump pack will automatically shut down after 30 seconds of continuous use.

Additionally this power will deactivate most powers upon activation. This power also grants the you a measure of flight protection making you less likely to be knocked out of the sky by some enemy attacks.

powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.Alt_Cheetah_Travel_Power

powers.name: Prestige.Prestige_Travel.Alt_Panther_Travel_Power
